Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.11,0:00:52.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要遲到了  遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.21,0:00:58.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼…
