Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.77,0:01:14.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,遲·到·囉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.30,0:01:16.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  真遜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.26,0:01:17.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
