Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.11,0:01:23.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,基爾巴特老師
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.01,0:01:26.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  奧茲同學
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.64,0:01:29.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天一起吃午飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.62,0:01:32.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,學生和老師怎麼能…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.89,0:01:34.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這點小事沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.78,0:01:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我想和老師一起吃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.84,0:01:39.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以做了便當帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.54,0:01:40.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,便當？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.56,0:01:43.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  是我精心製作的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.85,0:01:45.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,特製烤肉便當
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.27,0:01:47.27,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（肉骨頭  牛背肉  特製烤肉  裡脊肉  五分熟）
