Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.78,0:01:57.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是這個問題…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.48,0:01:59.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我在屋頂等您
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.88,0:02:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我都說了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.85,0:02:06.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.16,0:02:12.13,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（潘多拉學園  網球社）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.07,0:02:09.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,潘多拉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.32,0:02:11.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,之心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.43,0:02:24.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一眼看上去像是個爽朗的轉校生  沒想到…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.24,0:02:24.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.39,0:02:27.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把基爾巴特老師還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.74,0:02:29.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你口氣還真大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.30,0:02:32.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是不認得這位大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:33.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不認得
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:34.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,唔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.67,0:02:37.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然不認得這個學園的老大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.10,0:02:40.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奧茲同學…不要管我了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.89,0:02:42.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不過是成了個教師
